obile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8abd7a112f42e9ddb6b277b65699d5ea84024880","tid":1854103,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"愈來愈廢"},{"pid":"1d8164aa4d300390960e68ec19f1c2be8a914b0b","tid":1854103,"uid":241628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭一日唔死睇黎都唔會封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febe655210dff6cdeb2e2edd695a3657120bfbac","tid":1854103,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d8164aa4d300390960e68ec19f1c2be8a914b0b","tid":1854103,"uid":241628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭一日唔死睇黎都唔會封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"已經變成敵我矛盾，就算醫護罷工都唔會封 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13a70bb7ba3677ae1637c65111c7b9a49699e73","tid":1854103,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"係，香港人就係奴性咁重<br />\n<br />\n不過，收皮啦樓主你條死阻膠"}]}